rComments: Professor does not how to teach. I mean, unless teaching means writing the text book on the board and reading it aloud with no original input (literally word for word)
Prof. Entezari is a great speaker and her lectures were very clear. Her exams were harder than expected but if you follow her preparation guidelines your would be fine.
The course is tough and I understand why some people would find it difficult to handle. I really enjoyed her classes and she was available for office hours and longer discussions after classes.
She gave us a final exam that takes about 10 hours to finish it. How can she expect us to finish it in 3 hours. She really needs to bell curve up our final grades..
